commit_message: Updated README with Quast output example.

Bash Wrapper for Trimmomatic

The bash script allows one to automate the trimming via Trimmomatic.

Script for Post-Trimming QC

The script was designed to assess the reads following trimming with trimmomatic.

Script for Pre-Trimming QC

The script was designed to assess the reads prior to trimming with trimmomatic.

Fix Platanus B for Single Isolates

The update allows Platanus_B script to handle single isolates. The script also contains a line, detailing example input.

Fix IDBA_UD for Single Isolates

The update allows IDBA_UD script to handle single isolates. The script also contains a line, detailing example input.
Combined script for genome assembly pipeline
